name: Under the Sea by Rachel Wood

metadata.name: You are Resilience
metadata.description:
Keep your anemones at bay with these five Life mantras:

-May you remember that your struggles lend you resilience.

-May you fiercely guard your heart and protect your peace.

-May you gain a stronger will and grit from every disappointment.

-May you have a willingness to feel your feelings, instead of pushing them down.

-May you admit when you are wrong and not feel like a failure when you do.
